Confirm delete operation

Are you sure you want to delete this Product Like Dislike?

import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { NgbActiveModal } from '@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap'; import { IProductLikeDislike } from '../product-like-dislike.model'; import { ProductLikeDislikeService } from '../service/product-like-dislike.service'; @Component({ templateUrl: './product-like-dislike-delete-dialog.component.html', }) export class ProductLikeDislikeDeleteDialogComponent { productLikeDislike?: IProductLikeDislike; constructor(protected productLikeDislikeService: ProductLikeDislikeService, protected activeModal: NgbActiveModal) {} cancel(): void { this.activeModal.dismiss(); } confirmDelete(id: number): void { this.productLikeDislikeService.delete(id).subscribe(() => { this.activeModal.close('deleted'); }); } }
